      <abstract >This pastor's group was comprised of
        United Church of Christ members from the New England and New York regions who met annually
        to discuss and study a theme or topic. Contains publicity brochures and, minutes, and
        working files for the yearly study conference spanning from 1980 through 2000.</abstract>
