    </acqinfo>
    <bioghist >
      <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
      <p>From the context of the files, the purpose of the organization was to meet once a year at
        Springfield, Massachusetts, Old First Church, in February to discuss a theme selected by the
        planning committee. The members were within the United Church of Christ from New England and
        New York. The group has disbanded.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent >
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>Contains publicity brochures and, minutes, and working files for the yearly study
        conference spanning from 1980 through 2000.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement >
      <head>Arrangement</head>
      <p>This collection maintains the original order in which the records were given to the
        library.</p>
